    {
      "text": "A 35-year-old electrician presents with a 3-cm deep laceration to the dorsal hand sustained 6 hours ago while working with rusted electrical conduit. The wound has jagged edges with embedded metal debris. The patient recalls receiving childhood vaccinations and last received a tetanus booster during military service 7 years ago. After thorough irrigation and debridement, the wound requires suture closure. What is the next most appropriate step in tetanus prophylaxis?",
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": 1,
          "text": "Administer tetanus immunoglobulin only"
        },
        {
          "id": 2,
          "text": "Administer tetanus immunoglobulin and tetanus vaccine"
        },
        {
          "id": 3,
          "text": "Administer tetanus vaccine"
        },
        {
          "id": 4,
          "text": "Obtain tetanus antibody titers"
        },
        {
          "id": 5,
          "text": "No tetanus prophylaxis required"
        }
      ],
      "correct_choice_id": 3,
      "solution": "<div><h4 style='color: #f87171; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 16px; font-size: 1.125rem;'>A) INCORRECT:</h4>\n<a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=ef0xO2&anker=Z53fac39cf4be8bccfaff7c41a9b82f82\" data-learningcard-id=\"ef0xO2\" data-anker=\"Z53fac39cf4be8bccfaff7c41a9b82f82\" data-section-id=\"Af0RK2\" data-sememe-id=\"ddboKs\">Tetanus immunoglobulin</a> alone is never appropriate for <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=ef0xO2&anker=Zbd9d83ae0dba35a04ce3302d35d73835\" data-learningcard-id=\"ef0xO2\" data-anker=\"Zbd9d83ae0dba35a04ce3302d35d73835\" data-section-id=\"-f0DK2\" data-sememe-id=\"260T4S\">tetanus prophylaxis</a>. When indicated, <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=x50Emg&anker=Zcafc1c81671c54115ab5d77c08d696a0\" data-learningcard-id=\"x50Emg\" data-anker=\"Zcafc1c81671c54115ab5d77c08d696a0\" data-section-id=\"R_XlL00\" data-sememe-id=\"1fY2Oo\">immunoglobulin</a> must be given in combination with <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=ef0xO2&anker=Z5460f4ddce01d0b477da26e3b711cbc4\" data-learningcard-id=\"ef0xO2\" data-anker=\"Z5460f4ddce01d0b477da26e3b711cbc4\" data-section-id=\"-f0DK2\" data-sememe-id=\"U60b4S\">tetanus vaccine</a> to both provide immediate <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=_m05Rg&anker=Z074e24ca6749d89f915157e0041ec586\" data-learningcard-id=\"_m05Rg\" data-anker=\"Z074e24ca6749d89f915157e0041ec586\" data-section-id=\"eyXxV00\" data-sememe-id=\"UdYb6L\">passive immunity</a> and stimulate <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=_m05Rg&anker=Z857eba48e972c62e14b899278fa2799c\" data-learningcard-id=\"_m05Rg\" data-anker=\"Z857eba48e972c62e14b899278fa2799c\" data-section-id=\"VyXGV00\" data-sememe-id=\"0mXeVA\">active immunity</a>.</div><div><h4 style='color: #f87171; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 16px; font-size: 1.125rem;'>B) INCORRECT:</h4>\n<a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=ef0xO2&anker=Z53fac39cf4be8bccfaff7c41a9b82f82\" data-learningcard-id=\"ef0xO2\" data-anker=\"Z53fac39cf4be8bccfaff7c41a9b82f82\" data-section-id=\"Af0RK2\" data-sememe-id=\"ddboKs\">Tetanus immunoglobulin</a> is only indicated for patients with unknown <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=_m05Rg&anker=Zce79039ee0c9c756b2e006d3be169afc\" data-learningcard-id=\"_m05Rg\" data-anker=\"Zce79039ee0c9c756b2e006d3be169afc\" data-sememe-id=\"IL0Y_g\">vaccination</a> history or fewer than 3 documented doses when presenting with <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=ef0xO2&anker=Zdbc68adc8f0a20b123e12e6ce7544572\" data-learningcard-id=\"ef0xO2\" data-anker=\"Zdbc68adc8f0a20b123e12e6ce7544572\" data-section-id=\"-f0DK2\" data-sememe-id=\"A7dRor0\">tetanus-prone wounds</a>. This patient has adequate prior <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=_m05Rg&anker=Z2148e752962519f526f80b9aae6e8e2f\" data-learningcard-id=\"_m05Rg\" data-anker=\"Z2148e752962519f526f80b9aae6e8e2f\" data-section-id=\"KRcULX0\" data-sememe-id=\"M0XMg9\">immunization</a> based on childhood series plus military booster.</div><div><h4 style='color: #34d399; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 16px; font-size: 1.125rem;'>C) CORRECT:</h4>Correct -- This patient has a <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=ef0xO2&anker=Z72bdcc96970d33c72123484affff942d\" data-learningcard-id=\"ef0xO2\" data-anker=\"Z72bdcc96970d33c72123484affff942d\" data-sememe-id=\"7j04bT\">tetanus</a>-<a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=xo0EVS&anker=Z83bcbb5238240a9eec9b326afed139c9\" data-learningcard-id=\"xo0EVS\" data-anker=\"Z83bcbb5238240a9eec9b326afed139c9\" data-section-id=\"h_ccLU0\">prone</a> wound (deep <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=ph0LUf&anker=Z0e098a92252f6708b918be9f7214b8c0\" data-learningcard-id=\"ph0LUf\" data-anker=\"Z0e098a92252f6708b918be9f7214b8c0\" data-section-id=\"cOcarc0\" data-sememe-id=\"UlWbwl0\">laceration</a> with embedded metal debris from rusted material) and most recently received a <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=ef0xO2&anker=Z72bdcc96970d33c72123484affff942d\" data-learningcard-id=\"ef0xO2\" data-anker=\"Z72bdcc96970d33c72123484affff942d\" data-sememe-id=\"7j04bT\">tetanus</a> booster 7 years ago. <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=ef0xO2&anker=Z5460f4ddce01d0b477da26e3b711cbc4\" data-learningcard-id=\"ef0xO2\" data-anker=\"Z5460f4ddce01d0b477da26e3b711cbc4\" data-section-id=\"-f0DK2\" data-sememe-id=\"U60b4S\">Tetanus vaccine</a> alone is indicated for patients with <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=ef0xO2&anker=Zdbc68adc8f0a20b123e12e6ce7544572\" data-learningcard-id=\"ef0xO2\" data-anker=\"Zdbc68adc8f0a20b123e12e6ce7544572\" data-section-id=\"-f0DK2\" data-sememe-id=\"A7dRor0\">tetanus-prone wounds</a> and adequate prior <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=_m05Rg&anker=Z2148e752962519f526f80b9aae6e8e2f\" data-learningcard-id=\"_m05Rg\" data-anker=\"Z2148e752962519f526f80b9aae6e8e2f\" data-section-id=\"KRcULX0\" data-sememe-id=\"M0XMg9\">immunization</a> (≥ 3 doses) and whose last dose was ≥ 5 years ago.</div><div><h4 style='color: #f87171; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 16px; font-size: 1.125rem;'>D) INCORRECT:</h4>\n<a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=ef0xO2&anker=Z72bdcc96970d33c72123484affff942d\" data-learningcard-id=\"ef0xO2\" data-anker=\"Z72bdcc96970d33c72123484affff942d\" data-sememe-id=\"7j04bT\">Tetanus</a> <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=x50Emg&anker=Zcafc1c81671c54115ab5d77c08d696a0\" data-learningcard-id=\"x50Emg\" data-anker=\"Zcafc1c81671c54115ab5d77c08d696a0\" data-section-id=\"R_XlL00\" data-sememe-id=\"1fY2Oo\">antibody</a> <span data-sememe-id=\"3b1St20\">titers</span> are not routinely used for <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=WQ0PEf&anker=Z1a712230b67b35ad0db4b96d5bc7426e\" data-learningcard-id=\"WQ0PEf\" data-anker=\"Z1a712230b67b35ad0db4b96d5bc7426e\" data-section-id=\"Ry1lUj0\" data-sememe-id=\"rdWfr40\">post-exposure prophylaxis</a> decisions. Management is based on documented <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=_m05Rg&anker=Zce79039ee0c9c756b2e006d3be169afc\" data-learningcard-id=\"_m05Rg\" data-anker=\"Zce79039ee0c9c756b2e006d3be169afc\" data-sememe-id=\"IL0Y_g\">vaccination</a> history and wound characteristics. Obtaining <span data-sememe-id=\"3b1St20\">titers</span> delays appropriate treatment.</div><div><h4 style='color: #f87171; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 16px; font-size: 1.125rem;'>E) INCORRECT:</h4>This patient's deep wound with embedded metal debris from rusted material constitutes a <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=ef0xO2&anker=Z72bdcc96970d33c72123484affff942d\" data-learningcard-id=\"ef0xO2\" data-anker=\"Z72bdcc96970d33c72123484affff942d\" data-sememe-id=\"7j04bT\">tetanus</a>-<a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=xo0EVS&anker=Z83bcbb5238240a9eec9b326afed139c9\" data-learningcard-id=\"xo0EVS\" data-anker=\"Z83bcbb5238240a9eec9b326afed139c9\" data-section-id=\"h_ccLU0\">prone</a> wound. For <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=ef0xO2&anker=Zdbc68adc8f0a20b123e12e6ce7544572\" data-learningcard-id=\"ef0xO2\" data-anker=\"Zdbc68adc8f0a20b123e12e6ce7544572\" data-section-id=\"-f0DK2\" data-sememe-id=\"A7dRor0\">tetanus-prone wounds</a>, <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=ef0xO2&anker=Z5460f4ddce01d0b477da26e3b711cbc4\" data-learningcard-id=\"ef0xO2\" data-anker=\"Z5460f4ddce01d0b477da26e3b711cbc4\" data-section-id=\"-f0DK2\" data-sememe-id=\"U60b4S\">tetanus vaccine</a> is required when the last dose was ≥ 5 years ago.</div>",
